g\",\"description\":\"Ensuring healthy lives and promoting well-being for all at all ages\",\"icon\":\"üè•\",\"color\":\"#ef4444\",\"focus\":\"Health & Wellness\"},{\"id\":\"2\",\"number\":7,\"title\":\"Affordable and Clean Energy\",\"description\":\"Ensuring access to affordable, reliable, sustainable and modern energy\",\"icon\":\"‚ö°\",\"color\":\"#f59e0b\",\"focus\":\"Clean Energy\"},{\"id\":\"3\",\"number\":8,\"title\":\"Decent Work and Economic Growth\",\"description\":\"Promoting sustained, inclusive and sustainable economic growth\",\"icon\":\"üíº\",\"color\":\"#10b981\",\"focus\":\"Economic Development\"},{\"id\":\"4\",\"number\":11,\"title\":\"Sustainable Cities and Communities\",\"description\":\"Making cities and human settlements inclusive, safe, resilient and sustainable\",\"icon\":\"üèôÔ∏è\",\"color\":\"#f97316\",\"focus\":\"Urban Development\"},{\"id\":\"5\",\"number\":12,\"title\":\"Responsible Consumption and Production\",\"description\":\"Ensuring sustainable consumption and production patterns\",\"icon\":\"‚ôªÔ∏è\",\"color\":\"#eab308\",\"focus\":\"Resource Management\"},{\"id\":\"6\",\"number\":13,\"title\":\"Climate Action\",\"description\":\"Taking urgent action to combat climate change and its impacts\",\"icon\":\"üå°Ô∏è\",\"color\":\"#06b6d4\",\"focus\":\"Climate Change\"},{\"id\":\"7\",\"number\":15,\"title\":\"Life on Land\",\"description\":\"Protecting, restoring and promoting sustainable use of terrestrial ecosystems\",\"icon\":\"üå≥\",\"color\":\"#22c55e\",\"focus\":\"Biodiversity\"},{\"id\":\"8\",\"number\":17,\"title\":\"Partnerships for the Goals\",\"description\":\"Strengthening the means of implementation and revitalizing the global partnership\",\"icon\":\"ü§ù\",\"color\":\"#3b82f6\",\"focus\":\"Global Cooperation\"}],\"backgroundColor\":\"#1e3a8a\",\"textColor\":\"#f1f5f9\",\"titleColor\":\"#f1f5f9\",\"accentColor\":\"#60a5fa\",\"globeColor\":\"#dbeafe\"},\"backgroundColor\":\"#393a3c\"},{\"id\":\"environment-sustainability-commitment\",\"type\":\"environment-sustainability-commitment\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Our Commitment\",\"description1\":\"Sustainability is our pledge to build responsibly, act consciously, and leave a positive legacy. By integrating environmental intelligence with innovative technologies and human-centered design, RAUS delivers solutions that support climate resilience, ecological balance, and long-term community prosperity.\",\"description2\":\"We believe that shaping tomorrow begins with the actions we take today‚Äîand we remain committed to creating places where people thrive, ecosystems flourish, and future generations are protected.\",\"commitments\":[{\"id\":\"1\",\"quote\":\"Building responsibly means creating spaces that not only serve today\'s needs but protect tomorrow\'s possibilities.\",\"author\":\"RAUS Leadership\",\"role\":\"Environmental Stewardship\",\"icon\":\"üå±\",\"color\":\"#10b981\"},{\"id\":\"2\",\"quote\":\"Every project is an opportunity to advance sustainability and create lasting positive impact on our communities.\",\"author\":\"RAUS Team\",\"role\":\"Sustainable Development\",\"icon\":\"‚ôªÔ∏è\",\"color\":\"#3b82f6\"},{\"id\":\"3\",\"quote\":\"Innovation and environmental responsibility go hand in hand in shaping the future of our built environment.\",\"author\":\"RAUS Vision\",\"role\":\"Climate Action\",\"icon\":\"üåç\",\"color\":\"#f59e0b\"}],\"backgroundColor\":\"#f8fafc\",\"textColor\":\"#1f2937\",\"titleColor\":\"#1f2937\",\"accentColor\":\"#059669\",\"quoteColor\":\"#374151\"}}]', '2025-11-21 14:33:23', 'raus@gmail.com', 0, NULL),
('1763962042407', '1763141252163', '[{\"id\":\"hero-3-1\",\"type\":\"at-a-glance-hero\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"At a Glance\",\"subtitle\":\"\",\"text\":\"\",\"description\":\"A snapshot\\n of our journey, expertise, and \\nimpact\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?w=1600\",\"fontSize\":\"4rem\",\"color\":\"red\",\"backgroundImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1763148114007-925825.jpg\",\"backgroundVideo\":\"\",\"alignment\":\"center\",\"titleColor\":\"white\"}},{\"id\":\"who-we-are-3-2-1\",\"type\":\"who-we-are\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Who We Are\",\"text\":\"RAUS Integrated Project Management Services LLC is a dynamic, multi-disciplinary solutions partner founded in 2021 and headquartered in the UAE, with a fast-growing footprint in Tanzania, Nigeria, and the broader Middle East. We‚Äôre not your typical consultancy. RAUS is purpose-built to redefine how future-ready environments are imagined, developed, and optimized. From state-of-the-art infrastructure and digital ecosystems to sustainable architecture, ergonomic design, and comprehensive fit-out services, we connect ambition with precision. By integrating diverse technical expertise under one roof, we ensure a seamless, single-source solution that respects deadlines, enhances quality, and drives innovation at every stage.\",\"fontSize\":\"1.125rem\",\"color\":\"#414042\",\"sectionAlignment\":\"right\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://7exy4hnlmwjqhh3r.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/AtGlanceIntegratedProject-min.jpg\",\"titleColor\":\"#000\",\"textColor\":\"#3f3f3f\"}},{\"id\":\"who-we-are-3-2-2\",\"type\":\"who-we-are\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"What is Integrated Project Management ?\",\"text\":\"Integrated Project Management (IPM) is a comprehensive methodology that aligns project objectives with an organization‚Äôs strategic goals, ensuring all project components‚Äîfrom scope and schedule to resources and stakeholders‚Äîare coordinated effectively. It integrates different disciplines (like design, engineering, procurement, and construction) to streamline communication, reduce risks, and achieve better outcomes.\",\"fontSize\":\"1.125rem\",\"color\":\"#FFFFF\",\"sectionAlignment\":\"left\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://7exy4hnlmwjqhh3r.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/AtGlanceWhoWeAre-min.jpg\",\"titleColor\":\"#000\",\"textColor\":\"#3f3f3f\"}},{\"id\":\"dual-header-img-3-3\",\"type\":\"dual-header-img\",\"content\":{\"smallHeader\":\"Community & Society\",\"bigHeader\":\"Shaping the Future, One Community at a Time\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://7exy4hnlmwjqhh3r.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/AtGlanceShapingFuture-min.jpg\",\"description\":\"\",\"showButton\":false,\"showScrollIndicator\":false,\"overlayOpacity\":0.3}},{\"id\":\"home-services-3-4\",\"type\":\"at-a-glance-service\",\"content\":{\"0\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"iconType\":\"lucide\",\"iconName\":\"Home\",\"title\":\"Real Estate & Construction\",\"description\":\"Shaping sustainable, inclusive and future-ready environments\"},\"1\":{\"id\":\"2\",\"iconType\":\"lucide\",\"iconName\":\"Globe\",\"title\":\"Digital Transformation\",\"description\":\"Connecting architecture, tech and operations for smarter spaces\"},\"2\":{\"id\":\"3\",\"iconType\":\"lucide\",\"iconName\":\"Users\",\"title\":\"Strategic Consulting & Advisory Solutions\",\"description\":\"Driving strategic roadmaps for infrastructure, urban planning and digital growth\"},\"3\":{\"id\":\"4\",\"iconType\":\"lucide\",\"iconName\":\"Truck\",\"title\":\"Mobility & Transport Networks\",\"description\":\"Holistic transport planning using digital innovation for better connectivity and resilience\"},\"4\":{\"id\":\"5\",\"iconType\":\"lucide\",\"iconName\":\"BarChart3\",\"title\":\"Project Coordination & Approval Standards\",\"description\":\"End-to-end oversight with centralized management and approvals\"},\"title\":\"Shaping Better Cities\",\"subtitle\":\"Integrating Responsibility, Inclusivity and Collabora