('1763984178353', '1763141252163', '[{\"id\":\"hero-3-1\",\"type\":\"at-a-glance-hero\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"At a Glance\",\"subtitle\":\"\",\"text\":\"\",\"description\":\"A snapshot of our journey, expertise, and  impact\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?w=1600\",\"fontSize\":\"4rem\",\"color\":\"red\",\"backgroundImage\":\"https://jalgzgoha9oynfjc.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/image/1763148114007-925825.jpg\",\"backgroundVideo\":\"\",\"alignment\":\"center\",\"titleColor\":\"white\"}},{\"id\":\"who-we-are-3-2-1\",\"type\":\"who-we-are\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Who We Are\",\"text\":\"RAUS Integrated Project Management Services LLC is a dynamic, multi-disciplinary solutions partner founded in 2021 and headquartered in the UAE, with a fast-growing footprint in Tanzania, Nigeria, and the broader Middle East. We‚Äôre not your typical consultancy. RAUS is purpose-built to redefine how future-ready environments are imagined, developed, and optimized. From state-of-the-art infrastructure and digital ecosystems to sustainable architecture, ergonomic design, and comprehensive fit-out services, we connect ambition with precision. By integrating diverse technical expertise under one roof, we ensure a seamless, single-source solution that respects deadlines, enhances quality, and drives innovation at every stage.\",\"fontSize\":\"1.125rem\",\"color\":\"#414042\",\"sectionAlignment\":\"right\",\"imageUrl\":\"https://7exy4hnlmwjqhh3r.public.blob.vercel-storage.com/AtGlanceIntegratedProject-min.jpg\",\"titleColor\":\"#000\",\"textColor\":\"#3f3f3f\"}},{\"id\":\"who-we-are-3-2-2\",\"type\":\"who-we-are\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"What is Integrated Project Management ?\",\"text\":\"Integrated Project Management (IPM) is a comprehensive methodology that aligns project objectives with an organization‚Äôs strategic goals, ensuring all project components‚Äîfrom scope and schedule to resources and stakeholders‚Äîare coordinated effecti