bustling corporate campuses to vibrant public spaces, our work is guided by a simple yet powerful principle: build places where people feel a sense of belonging, inspiration, and pride\",\"overlayOpacity\":0.9},\"order\":5},{\"id\":\"text-3-5\",\"type\":\"text\",\"content\":{\"title\":\"Every space we create is a promise‚Äîa commitment to the people who live, work, and play there. Together, we‚Äôre not just shaping structures; we‚Äôre shaping futures.\",\"text\":\"\",\"fontSize\":\"1.5rem\",\"color\":\"#db0000\",\"alignment\":\"center\"},\"order\":6},{\"id\":\"value-card-3-6\",\"type\":\"value-card\",\"content\":{\"0\":{\"id\":\"1\",\"value\":\"90%\",\"valueColor\":\"#EF4130\",\"description\":\"Project Success Rate\"},\"items\":[{\"value\":\"78%\",\"valueColor\":\"#ff2d1a\",\"description\":\"of customers prefer brands that prioritize social responsibility\"},{\"value\":\"25%\",\"valueColor\":\"#0074cc\",\"description\":\"Increase in social interaction in communities with quality public spaces.\"},{\"value\":\"20%\",\"valueColor\":\"#37008a\",\"description\":\"reduction in project delays through local partnerships\"},{\"value\":\"60%\",\"valueColor\":\"#132a86\",\"description\":\" of employees feel more engaged in companies with strong CSR values.\"}],\"columns\":{\"base\":4,\"sm\":4,\"md\":4,\"lg\":4,\"xl\":5},\"title\":\" \",\"subtitle\":\"We believe that the true measure of progress is how it uplifts the people and communities it touches. From bustling corporate campuses to vibrant public spaces, our work is guided by a simple yet powerful principle: build places where people feel a sense of belonging, inspiration, and pride\",\"accentColor\":\"#3b82f6\",\"textBackgroundColor\":\"#ff0a0a\"},\"order\":7}]', '2025-11-24 18:25:42', 'raus@gmail.com', 0, NULL);
